":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:54:15.000Z","msg":"咁咩牌子先好？<br />\n精工？"},{"pid":"43f2ffc58146a32fd5d9881b1bf1451098b4bb12","tid":138754,"uid":2506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咩牌子先好？<br />\n精工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩牌子差得過Titus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機械 要平咪精工<br />\n有錢買靚少少都好耐用"},{"pid":"ceedaaffe025149ffc5d0fcf539f66cfa25983b4","tid":138754,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zf37Vg5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzf37Vg5.jpg&h=e0332595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概12月28買，2200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，已經壞左一次，而家個機芯好快就要上一次鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申外國jj"},{"pid":"6ac18772beb7220db6cadce3632f3757e9c46400","tid":138754,"uid":74832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁咩牌子先好？<br />\n精工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩牌子差得過Titus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機械 要平咪精工<br />\n有錢買靚少少都好耐用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有好多錶post爬下文都可以知下。"},{"pid":"175a8009696a1cfb9ba5b9e82c7b4413f57e176b","tid":138754,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁咩牌子先好？<br />\n精工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩牌子差得過Titus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機械 要平咪精工<br />\n有錢買靚少少都好耐用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有好多錶post爬下文都可以知下。</blockquote><br />\n有錶post嘅地方必有光巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257947945d5842f1f4eef5d1055681bcfd669e07","tid":138754,"uid":43943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:24:57.000Z","ms